OL,3,CWe must give youngsters way out of
OL,4,Cviolence, says Cleverly amid knives
OL,5,Ccrackdown
OL,7,FZombie-style knives were first banned
OL,8,Fin 2016 but ministers hope these
OL,9,Ftighter measures will stop some
OL,10,Fretailers being able to sell dangerous
OL,11,Fknives and machetes without breaking
OL,12,Fthe law.
OL,14,FAhead of the announcement Mr Cleverly
OL,15,Fmet police chiefs in Kent to discuss
OL,16,Fyouth violence prevention projects and
OL,17,Fjoined officers on a foot patrol of
OL,18,FGravesend town centre.
