OL,3,CWe must give youngsters way out of
OL,4,Cviolence, says Cleverly amid knives
OL,5,Ccrackdown
OL,7,FLabour said the changes had already
OL,8,Fbeen promised by six Conservative home
OL,9,Fsecretaries and "loopholes" mean they
OL,10,Fdo not go far enough to be a
OL,11,F"comprehensive ban".
OL,13,FAsked why the legislation has taken so
OL,14,Flong, Mr Cleverly said: "We have
OL,15,Falready taken action to make the
OL,16,Fcarrying of zombie knives illegal.
