OL,3,CWe must give youngsters way out of
OL,4,Cviolence, says Cleverly amid knives
OL,5,Ccrackdown
OL,7,FAnnouncing the measures, he added: "We
OL,8,Fcannot let them be sold to children,
OL,9,Fand we must give young people a way
OL,10,Fout of violence."
OL,12,FThe ban, coming into force from
OL,13,FSeptember, will make it illegal to
OL,14,Fpossess, sell, manufacture or
OL,15,Ftransport these zombie-style knives
OL,16,Fand machetes.
