OL,4,Cviolence, says Cleverly amid knives
OL,5,Ccrackdown
OL,7,FSo-called zombie knives are currently
OL,8,Fdefined by the Government as a blade
OL,9,Fwith "a cutting edge, a serrated edge
OL,10,Fand images or words suggesting it is
OL,11,Fused for violence".
OL,13,FA surrender scheme is also being put
OL,14,Fin place for people to give up their
OL,15,Fweapons before the law comes into
OL,16,Fforce without any consequences.
