OL,3,CWe must give youngsters way out of
OL,4,Cviolence, says Cleverly amid knives
OL,5,Ccrackdown
OL,7,FMr Cleverly told the PA news agency
OL,8,Fthe steps being taken this week are
OL,9,F"further strengthening" the
OL,10,FGovernment's ability to tackle knife
OL,11,Fcrime.
OL,13,FHe added: "We'll add to what has been
OL,14,Fa success story since 2019. We've seen
OL,15,Fa very significant reduction in knife
OL,16,Fcrime over that time.
OL,18,F"We have a plan which is working and
OL,19,Fdriving down knife crime."
