OL,3,CWe must give youngsters way out of
OL,4,Cviolence, says Cleverly amid knives
OL,5,Ccrackdown
OL,7,F"Dangerous weapons like ninja swords,
OL,8,Fwhich have been used to kill
OL,9,Fteenagers, will still be available on
OL,10,FBritain's streets.
OL,12,F"Still, law-breaking online platforms
OL,13,Fwho profit from these illegal sales
OL,14,Fare being let off with a slap on the
OL,15,Fwrist instead of facing criminal
OL,16,Fsanctions. Labour would close these
OL,17,Fglaring loopholes in the Government's
OL,18,Fplans".
