OL,7,FActor Idris Elba has also put pressure
OL,8,Fon the Government through launching
OL,9,Fthe Don't Stop Your Future campaign
OL,10,Fcalling for the immediate banning of
OL,11,Fmachetes and zombie knives.
OL,13,FThe legislation announcement comes as
OL,14,FLabour announced a #100 million youth
OL,15,Fprogramme to tackle knife crime.
